high_descs: Turn left and face the counter just to the right of the fridge.
Pick up the clear glass.
Take a step to the left and face the fridge.
Put the glass in the fridge to the left of the apple. Wait a moment and take it out of the fridge again.
Turn around and walk to the sink.
Put the glass in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled glass in the sink.

high_descs: Turn left ninety degrees, walk forward, turn left ninety degrees to face the white counter top.
Pick up the glass on the counter top close to the edge.
Turn left ninety degrees, walk forward to fridge, turn right ninety degrees to face fridge,
Open the fridge door, place glass inside fridge, close fridge door, open fridge door, remove glass from fridge, close fridge door.
Turn right ninety degrees, walk forward to stove, turn right ninety degrees to face sink, walk forward to sink.
Place glass in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a glass from the white counter top, into the sink.

high_descs: Turn left and head forward then make a quick left after the fridge to face the counter to the right of the fridge
Pick up the clear glass that sitting on the counter
Step in front of the fridge that is on your left
Open the fridge and place the glass on the middle shelf to the left of the apple then close the door.  Then open the fridge door and take the glass from the middle shelf and close the door
Turn right and walk to the stove, then turn right and walk to the sink
Place the glass on the ride side of the sink
anns.task_desc: Place a glass into a sink

high_descs: Walk forward, then turn left and walk over to the counter to the left of the oven.
Pick up the glass off of the counter.
Turn left and walk towards the door, then turn right to face the fridge.
Open the fridge door and put the glass inside then close the fridge door, after a couple seconds open the fridge back up and remove the glass, then close the fridge door.
Turn right and walk forward, then turn right and walk over to the sink.
Put the chilled glass in the sink basin.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled glass in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around, walk to the kitchen counter with the salt on top.
Pick up the glass from the counter.
Turn left, walk to the refrigerator
Open the refrigerator, put the glass inside the refrigerator, close the refrigerator, wait 3 seconds, open the refrigerator, take the glass out of the refrigerator
Close the refrigerator, turn around, walk to the sink
Put the glass in the sink
anns.task_desc: Cool the glass off in the refrigerator, put the glass in the sink.
